  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill them all is a linear narrative game where you play a mercenary who will be deployed on Serenity Island. The island is facing a serious epidemic and does not have the military capabilities to manage the situation properly. You will be mandated to carry out various missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931400/extras/c929a72c32cf3bb034a65bf57ea63db2.webp?t=1748266606\" width=800 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931400/extras/e1f8dc279c5ca37aba6c56942965b40f.webp?t=1748266606\" width=800 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931400/extras/48e6666151fb8f86358d22ae6c2845b6.poster.avif?t=1748266606\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931400/extras/48e6666151fb8f86358d22ae6c2845b6.webm?t=1748266606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931400/extras/48e6666151fb8f86358d22ae6c2845b6.mp4?t=1748266606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The title says it all </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931400/extras/c929a72c32cf3bb034a65bf57ea63db2.webp?t=1748266606\" width=800 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"